WEBVTT

00:02.017 --> 00:05.321
Cheers is filmed before
a live studio audience.

00:06.156 --> 00:08.157
Hey, what're you doing there, Norm?

00:08.157 --> 00:10.160
Oh, Vera signed me up to give a speech

00:10.160 --> 00:11.661
at her Women's Auxiliary Club.

00:11.661 --> 00:12.662
(laughs)

00:12.662 --> 00:14.164
I hate public speaking.

00:14.164 --> 00:15.665
Yeah, you're not alone there, pal.

00:15.665 --> 00:17.167
Well, it's awful, you know.

00:17.167 --> 00:18.168
You're standing there

00:18.168 --> 00:20.170
in front of a group
of total strangers...

00:20.170 --> 00:22.672
palms sweating, your throat dry,

00:22.672 --> 00:24.674
your mouth feels like
it's full of cotton.

00:24.674 --> 00:26.042
your knees practically buckling.

00:26.042 --> 00:28.011
It can be a miserable
experience. I tell you.

00:28.011 --> 00:29.012
So what's the topic?

00:29.012 --> 00:32.015
"Poise: The Key to Success."

00:34.017 --> 00:37.437
(piano plays)

00:37.887 --> 00:40.190
? Making your way in the world today ?

00:40.190 --> 00:42.692
? Takes everything you've got ?

00:42.692 --> 00:46.196
? Taking a break from all your worries ?

00:46.196 --> 00:48.698
? Sure would help a lot ?

00:48.698 --> 00:51.701
? Wouldn't you like to get away? ?

00:54.454 --> 00:57.240
? Sometimes you want to go ?

00:57.240 --> 01:01.745
? Where everybody knows your name ?

01:01.745 --> 01:07.250
? And they're always glad you came ?

01:07.250 --> 01:09.252
? You want to be where you can see ?

01:09.252 --> 01:12.255
? Our troubles are all the same ?

01:12.255 --> 01:16.760
? You want to be where
everybody knows your name ?

01:17.761 --> 01:20.263
? You want to go where people know ?

01:20.263 --> 01:22.766
